#

Avocado Turkey Burger

25 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Gluten (from buns)

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Main Dish

Tags:

EasyHealthyComfort Food

Description

A juicy turkey burger topped with creamy avocado, served on a toasted bun for a deliciously satisfying meal.

Ingredients

  • ground turkey: 1 pound
  • avocado: 1 ripe
  • whole wheat burger buns: 4
  • lettuce leaves: 4
  • tomato slices: 1
  • red onion slices: 1
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • garlic powder: 1 teaspoon
